    {
      "id": "findings-page-purpose",
      "name": "Page Purpose",
      "description": "The Findings page aggregates issues discovered across task runs, organized by severity (critical, high, medium, low) and category. Users can search and filter findings, expand them to see full details including file paths and stack traces, resolve individual findings, or trigger auto-fix workflows to remediate issues automatically.",
